		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Very impressive for a heuristic method. <em>Super Mario Bros.</em> works OK, except the treetops in 1-3 look like a green log on top of the tree trunk. But it seems to treat the outdoor background in <em>The Legend of Zelda</em> as thick fog.<br /><br />I wonder what it does with <em>Dr. Mario</em> or any of <a href="https://shiru.untergrund.net/software.shtml" class="postlink">Shiru's games</a> or any of <a href="https://pineight.com/nes/" class="postlink">my games</a>.

		

